1
00:00:13,972 --> 00:00:15,849
SIRI ASLI NETFLIX

2
00:00:51,051 --> 00:00:53,970
WATAK, KEJADIAN, ORGANISASI,
DAN LATAR BELAKANG HANYA REKAAN

3
00:01:30,298 --> 00:01:31,298
Puan.

4
00:01:32,300 --> 00:01:33,343
Awak dah nak balik?

5
00:01:33,426 --> 00:01:35,345
Ya, terima kasih untuk hari ini.

6
00:01:35,428 --> 00:01:36,429
Pulang dengan selamat.

7
00:01:56,908 --> 00:01:57,909
Hei.

8
00:01:59,452 --> 00:02:01,454
SEKURITI

9
00:02:02,705 --> 00:02:04,082
Apa awak buat?

10
00:02:05,936 --> 00:02:06,936
Meronda.

11
00:02:06,960 --> 00:02:08,461
Kami ronda kawasan ini.

12
00:02:08,545 --> 00:02:10,296
Awak pastikan lampu pejabat ditutup.

13
00:02:14,717 --> 00:02:16,886
Saya tak pernah nampak dia.

14
00:02:17,011 --> 00:02:21,641
Dia kacukan Cina-Korea yang diupah
sebagai pengawal sandaran.

15
00:02:21,724 --> 00:02:24,811
Dia mahir seni bela diri dan senjata api.

16
00:03:06,811 --> 00:03:08,104
Puas saya cari awak.

17
00:03:09,898 --> 00:03:13,193
Awak cuma kata awak tinggal
di Cheongdam-dong, Gangnam-gu, Seoul.

18
00:03:14,777 --> 00:03:16,821
Awak tak beritahu alamat tepat.

19
00:03:20,658 --> 00:03:21,784
Awak tahu?

20
00:03:22,327 --> 00:03:25,288
Saya tak suka mimpi begini.

21
00:03:26,831 --> 00:03:30,460
Apabila terjaga nanti, saya tentu sedih.

22
00:03:32,295 --> 00:03:37,008
Walaupun awak pandang saya begitu,
saya tak gembira.

23
00:03:37,091 --> 00:03:38,676
Tapi ini bukan mimpi.

24
00:03:40,094 --> 00:03:41,262
Awak pasti?

25
00:03:42,847 --> 00:03:43,847
Ya.

26
00:04:06,829 --> 00:04:10,416
Macam mana awak boleh ke sini?

27
00:04:12,126 --> 00:04:13,419
Kenapa dengan muka awak?

28
00:04:14,379 --> 00:04:15,964
Awak cedera?

29
00:04:18,758 --> 00:04:19,801
Saya tak apa-apa.

30
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:36,276
<i>Ada lombong emas lama
yang digali semasa zaman Jepun.</i>

31
00:04:37,235 --> 00:04:39,237
<i>Kita boleh andaikan</i>

32
00:04:39,320 --> 00:04:41,864
<i>Cho Cheol Gang ikut jalan ini ke Selatan.</i>

33
00:04:43,032 --> 00:04:45,201
<i>Tapi, ia sangat sejuk.</i>

34
00:04:45,702 --> 00:04:49,205
<i>Disebabkan Cho Cheol Gang
telah gali hingga ke Selatan,</i>

35
00:04:49,289 --> 00:04:51,499
<i>ia boleh runtuh bila-bila masa.</i>

36
00:05:14,814 --> 00:05:17,150
<i>Untuk merentasi gua buatan
sepanjang 10 kilometer</i>

37
00:05:17,233 --> 00:05:20,278
<i>yang cuma muat untuk seorang itu,</i>

38
00:05:20,361 --> 00:05:23,698
<i>awak perlu bergerak 20 jam tanpa rehat.</i>

39
00:05:24,782 --> 00:05:26,576
<i>Jika awak selamat sampai ke hujung,</i>

40
00:05:37,211 --> 00:05:40,131
<i>ada gua semula jadi
yang mengunjur ke laut.</i>

41
00:06:39,482 --> 00:06:41,317
Saya takkan percaya

42
00:06:41,943 --> 00:06:44,445
jika awak kata awak tak apa-apa.

43
00:06:45,029 --> 00:06:46,155
Saya tak apa-apa.

44
00:06:47,698 --> 00:06:49,033
Tiada apa-apa berlaku.

45
00:07:12,849 --> 00:07:14,392
Tunggulah dia balik.

46
00:07:14,475 --> 00:07:17,353
Kenapa kita yang kena buat
malam-malam begini?

47
00:07:17,437 --> 00:07:21,023
Macam mana kalau rasanya berubah
kerana kita lewat?

48
00:07:24,777 --> 00:07:26,362
Sayang.

49
00:07:26,446 --> 00:07:27,697
Mari sekejap.

50
00:07:42,003 --> 00:07:44,005
POLIS

51
00:07:57,935 --> 00:07:59,103
Saya dah jumpa!

52
00:08:14,702 --> 00:08:17,580
Apa berlaku?

53
00:08:18,998 --> 00:08:20,958
Apa awak buat di sini?

54
00:08:22,793 --> 00:08:23,793
Awak…

55
00:08:24,962 --> 00:08:26,380
Belot Korea Utara kerana saya?

56
00:08:26,464 --> 00:08:27,464
Tidak.

57
00:08:28,424 --> 00:08:30,301
- Jadi, awak pengintip?
- Bukan.

58
00:08:30,551 --> 00:08:33,721
Jadi, awak akan berpindah terus ke sini?

59
00:08:34,388 --> 00:08:35,431
Mestilah tidak.

60
00:08:36,265 --> 00:08:37,433
Saya cuma melawat.

61
00:08:37,517 --> 00:08:40,811
Tak semudah merentasi Sungai Han.

62
00:08:41,395 --> 00:08:43,272
Awak tak boleh "lawat" Selatan

63
00:08:43,356 --> 00:08:44,815
dari negara asal awak.

64
00:08:44,899 --> 00:08:48,236
Lagipun, kalau mudah sangat
nak ke Selatan,

65
00:08:48,319 --> 00:08:50,154
kenapa saya terperangkap lama di sana?

66
00:08:50,947 --> 00:08:52,657
Tak mudah…

67
00:08:52,740 --> 00:08:53,741
Ibu bapa awak tahu?

68
00:08:54,325 --> 00:08:58,162
Ayah awak tentu marah.
Apa yang awak beritahu mereka?

69
00:08:59,330 --> 00:09:01,123
Saya nak mula jawab,

70
00:09:01,624 --> 00:09:03,084
jadi jangan tanya lagi.

71
00:09:03,209 --> 00:09:04,209
Baik.

72
00:09:14,595 --> 00:09:15,595
Cho Cheol Gang.

73
00:09:17,598 --> 00:09:19,058
Dia dah ada di sini.

74
00:09:19,642 --> 00:09:20,642
Apa?

75
00:09:20,685 --> 00:09:23,980
Dia sepatutnya dipenjarakan,

76
00:09:24,814 --> 00:09:26,649
tapi hilang semasa dipindahkan.

77
00:09:28,109 --> 00:09:30,695
Dia ke sini untuk buru awak.

78
00:09:31,529 --> 00:09:32,529
Saya?

79
00:09:34,991 --> 00:09:36,117
Jadi…

80
00:09:37,618 --> 00:09:42,164
Awak datang sebab risau
Cho Cheol Gang akan apa-apakan saya?

81
00:09:42,665 --> 00:09:45,459
Awak tempuhi semua itu kerana saya?

82
00:09:46,043 --> 00:09:47,420
Bukan cuma kerana awak.

83
00:09:48,421 --> 00:09:50,381
Dia takkan cuma serang awak.

84
00:09:51,048 --> 00:09:52,925
Dia nak guna awak untuk sabotaj saya

85
00:09:53,009 --> 00:09:54,760
dan seluruh keluarga saya.

86
00:09:54,844 --> 00:09:56,470
Saya datang untuk halang dia.

87
00:09:57,638 --> 00:09:59,348
Bukan cuma untuk lindungi awak.

88
00:10:02,184 --> 00:10:07,064
Jadi, bila awak kena balik ke sana?

89
00:10:08,107 --> 00:10:09,483
Selepas saya tangkap dia,

90
00:10:10,401 --> 00:10:11,527
walaupun malam ini.

91
00:10:13,279 --> 00:10:14,279
Selepas tangkap dia?

92
00:10:20,536 --> 00:10:22,496
Baiklah.

93
00:10:23,914 --> 00:10:27,335
Tapi jika saya sasaran utama dia,

94
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:29,754
misi utama awak
adalah lindungi saya.

95
00:10:31,130 --> 00:10:35,051
Untuk itu, awak kena tinggal dengan saya.

96
00:10:35,676 --> 00:10:36,677
Sentiasa di sisi saya.

97
00:10:38,888 --> 00:10:40,097
Selamat datang.

98
00:10:41,807 --> 00:10:42,807
Mari pergi.

99
00:10:46,998 --> 00:10:47,998
Saya tak sejuk.

100
00:10:48,022 --> 00:10:50,358
Bukan itu sebabnya.

101
00:10:51,108 --> 00:10:52,943
Korea Selatan menakutkan.

102
00:10:53,027 --> 00:10:55,696
Ada kamera keselamatan,
papan pemuka dan telefon.

103
00:10:55,780 --> 00:10:57,907
Sambungan internet di sini pula
terpantas di dunia.

104
00:10:57,990 --> 00:11:01,535
Gambar awak boleh tersebar
ke seluruh negara dalam 30 minit.

105
00:11:01,619 --> 00:11:03,579
Jadi, tutup muka awak.

106
00:11:04,497 --> 00:11:07,458
Jangan sampai orang nampak.

107
00:11:08,876 --> 00:11:11,170
Hati-hati bercakap.

108
00:11:11,796 --> 00:11:14,465
Kalau Perkhidmatan Perisikan Negara
dan polis

109
00:11:14,548 --> 00:11:18,427
dengar perbualan kita,
mereka pasti gempar.

110
00:11:19,679 --> 00:11:20,971
Kita tiada pilihan.

111
00:11:21,472 --> 00:11:25,726
Saya mesti pastikan
orang lain tak nampak awak

112
00:11:26,686 --> 00:11:29,855
dan tak dengar perbualan kita.

113
00:11:30,564 --> 00:11:33,818
Jadi saya kena cari tempat tertutup

114
00:11:34,276 --> 00:11:38,531
yang cuma kita saja yang tahu.

115
00:11:39,365 --> 00:11:40,365
Mari.

116
00:11:41,158 --> 00:11:42,326
Saya sorokkan awak.

117
00:11:54,088 --> 00:11:55,088
Ini…

118
00:11:55,548 --> 00:11:57,675
Inilah tempat tinggal saya.

119
00:12:02,471 --> 00:12:04,724
Harap awak selesa.

120
00:12:06,684 --> 00:12:07,684
Saya dah selesa.

121
00:12:09,353 --> 00:12:11,856
Awak nak mandi dulu?

122
00:12:14,692 --> 00:12:17,027
Kenapa? Tentu awak letih.

123
00:12:17,695 --> 00:12:20,573
Kenapa pandang saya begitu?

124
00:12:20,656 --> 00:12:21,907
Awak buat saya malu.

125
00:12:23,325 --> 00:12:24,493
Saya…

126
00:12:25,077 --> 00:12:28,539
Saya akan mandi nanti. Tak perlu suruh.

127
00:12:29,892 --> 00:12:30,892
Baiklah.

128
00:12:30,916 --> 00:12:33,419
Awak lapar? Nak makan?

129
00:12:42,094 --> 00:12:43,929
- Apa yang awak makan?
- Terkejut saya.

130
00:12:45,556 --> 00:12:46,556
Saya…

131
00:12:49,226 --> 00:12:51,562
Awak asyik berlagak kaya.

132
00:12:53,939 --> 00:12:55,941
Kenapa tiada makanan di rumah?

133
00:12:58,068 --> 00:12:59,111
Sebab…

134
00:13:00,738 --> 00:13:03,032
Bukankah saya dah cakap?

135
00:13:03,115 --> 00:13:05,409
Saya digelar Puteri Cerewet.

136
00:13:08,078 --> 00:13:09,705
Sedapnya.

137
00:13:11,999 --> 00:13:13,626
Tapi awak kuat makan.

138
00:13:13,709 --> 00:13:18,297
Saya hanya makan tiga suapan.

139
00:13:18,380 --> 00:13:19,757
Sejak kenal awak,

140
00:13:20,257 --> 00:13:22,551
awak tak pernah makan kurang tiga suap.

141
00:13:22,635 --> 00:13:25,012
Itu dalam situasi tertentu.

142
00:13:25,095 --> 00:13:27,139
Saya risau takkan dapat makan lagi,

143
00:13:27,223 --> 00:13:30,392
jadi saya makan untuk hidup.

144
00:13:31,185 --> 00:13:32,728
Kita boleh pesan. Nak makan apa?

145
00:13:32,812 --> 00:13:36,357
Piza? Masakan Cina? Ayam goreng?

146
00:13:37,358 --> 00:13:41,111
Kenapa ada banyak restoran ayam
di Selatan?

147
00:13:42,822 --> 00:13:44,240
Ramainya orang makan ayam.

148
00:13:46,492 --> 00:13:48,327
Berapa harganya?

149
00:13:48,410 --> 00:13:52,248
Tak kisahlah, tapi kita pasti tak mampu.

150
00:13:55,835 --> 00:13:57,253
Apa kamu buat di situ?

151
00:13:58,420 --> 00:13:59,420
Komrad!

152
00:13:59,922 --> 00:14:01,048
Hei!

153
00:14:02,174 --> 00:14:04,593
"Komrad"? Dah lupa latihan kita?

154
00:14:04,677 --> 00:14:06,470
Orang boleh dengar!

155
00:14:07,054 --> 00:14:09,056
Ya, saya akan cakap seperti orang di sini.

156
00:14:10,182 --> 00:14:11,183
Abang.

157
00:14:12,017 --> 00:14:14,687
Man Bok, cakap macam biasa.

158
00:14:18,607 --> 00:14:20,818
Baiklah. Cakaplah.

159
00:14:20,901 --> 00:14:22,653
Saya berpendapat

160
00:14:22,736 --> 00:14:25,781
kita patut anggap paha ayam
musuh ibu bapa kita

161
00:14:25,865 --> 00:14:27,533
dan makan hingga ia lenyap.

162
00:14:32,246 --> 00:14:33,956
Tapi dana kita terhad.

163
00:14:34,039 --> 00:14:36,792
Alangkah bagusnya kalau
kita segera jumpa Kapten Ri.

164
00:14:36,876 --> 00:14:39,712
Jika tidak, kita perlukan wang
untuk hidup di sini.

165
00:14:41,046 --> 00:14:43,173
Jadi, kita mesti berjimat.

166
00:15:01,233 --> 00:15:02,233
<i>Penghantaran!</i>

167
00:15:05,112 --> 00:15:06,112
Makanlah.

168
00:15:11,994 --> 00:15:14,538
- Kenapa?
- Adab orang Selatan.

169
00:15:14,622 --> 00:15:17,166
Apabila tuan rumah hidangkan makanan,

170
00:15:17,249 --> 00:15:19,710
minta tuan rumah makan dulu.

171
00:15:19,793 --> 00:15:21,378
Khabarnya, itu adab kamu.

172
00:15:22,922 --> 00:15:23,964
Tolonglah.

173
00:15:33,515 --> 00:15:34,934
Kenapa pandang begitu?

174
00:15:35,517 --> 00:15:37,353
Saya masih tak percaya.

175
00:15:37,436 --> 00:15:41,690
Awak duduk di sebelah saya, di rumah saya,

176
00:15:41,774 --> 00:15:43,400
dan makan dengan saya.

177
00:15:48,072 --> 00:15:50,032
Macam mana dengan keluarga awak?

178
00:15:53,035 --> 00:15:54,035
Baik-baik saja.

179
00:15:54,703 --> 00:15:56,288
Saya tahu itu yang awak risaukan.

180
00:15:56,914 --> 00:15:59,959
Awalnya, saya pun risau.

181
00:16:00,668 --> 00:16:02,378
Tapi, betul kata awak.

182
00:16:02,962 --> 00:16:03,962
Saya?

183
00:16:04,338 --> 00:16:05,714
Ya, betul kata awak.

184
00:16:06,340 --> 00:16:09,009
Benci macam mana pun,
keluarga tetap keluarga.

185
00:16:09,093 --> 00:16:12,805
Kami selalu bertengkar kerana tak sebulu,

186
00:16:12,888 --> 00:16:14,765
tapi apabila saya pulang,

187
00:16:15,557 --> 00:16:17,685
mereka gembira melihat saya.

188
00:16:18,143 --> 00:16:19,603
Jadi, semuanya okey.

189
00:16:20,521 --> 00:16:21,605
Baguslah.

190
00:16:22,314 --> 00:16:23,941
Saya baik-baik saja di sini.

191
00:16:24,024 --> 00:16:28,278
Saya teringin nak beritahu awak semua itu,

192
00:16:28,946 --> 00:16:33,951
tapi saya tak boleh e-mel
atau telefon awak.

193
00:16:34,994 --> 00:16:38,497
Sekarang, bolehlah saya beritahu.

194
00:16:39,498 --> 00:16:44,294
Jadi, tak perlu risaukan saya
di sana nanti.

195
00:16:56,765 --> 00:16:58,851
Tak perlu terkejut.

196
00:16:58,934 --> 00:17:01,729
Ini Republik Korea
dan saya bukan sesiapa di sini.

197
00:17:01,812 --> 00:17:04,565
Sistem keselamatan bangunan ini
cukup ketat.

198
00:17:09,445 --> 00:17:12,573
Kenapa mereka datang di waktu ini?

199
00:17:17,578 --> 00:17:18,578
Siapa mereka?

200
00:17:18,996 --> 00:17:23,667
Abang kedua dan isterinya.
Kenapa mereka datang begini lewat?

201
00:17:24,418 --> 00:17:26,712
Makanlah. Mereka akan balik sendiri.

202
00:17:31,633 --> 00:17:32,634
Dia keluar?

203
00:17:33,427 --> 00:17:36,096
Dia ada di rumah, cuma tak nak buka pintu.

204
00:17:37,014 --> 00:17:38,223
Saya tahu kodnya.

205
00:17:39,183 --> 00:17:40,225
Tekanlah.

206
00:17:46,148 --> 00:17:47,816
Betulkah sistem keselamatannya bagus?

207
00:17:47,900 --> 00:17:49,777
Tolong masuk ke bilik.

208
00:17:49,860 --> 00:17:51,695
Ambil jaket awak.

209
00:17:53,572 --> 00:17:54,698
Tak guna.

210
00:17:57,993 --> 00:18:00,662
Ini dikira menceroboh.

211
00:18:00,746 --> 00:18:03,332
Ini abang awak sendiri.

212
00:18:03,415 --> 00:18:06,251
- Awak nak ke mana?
- Kenapa sekat nombor kami?

213
00:18:06,335 --> 00:18:08,003
Siapa benarkan kamu masuk?

214
00:18:10,506 --> 00:18:11,632
Tak guna.

215
00:18:18,138 --> 00:18:20,682
Kenapa datang? Ada apa?

216
00:18:21,308 --> 00:18:22,392
Seri.

217
00:18:24,853 --> 00:18:26,355
Kami tahu semuanya.

218
00:18:27,208 --> 00:18:28,208
Tahu apa?

219
00:18:28,232 --> 00:18:30,609
Kami tahu awak ke mana sebenarnya.

220
00:18:32,277 --> 00:18:35,114
Awak tahu perkara yang saya tak tahu?

221
00:18:35,197 --> 00:18:38,408
Jangan pura-pura bodoh. Saya meluat.

222
00:18:39,409 --> 00:18:40,661
Awak di Korea Utara.

223
00:18:42,204 --> 00:18:43,622
Awak tokoh masyarakat.

224
00:18:43,705 --> 00:18:46,583
Macam mana kalau orang tahu?

225
00:18:47,084 --> 00:18:48,919
"Kemalangan. Saya tak ingat apa-apa."

226
00:18:49,419 --> 00:18:50,963
Awak asyik beri alasan,

227
00:18:51,046 --> 00:18:52,381
tapi tiada sesiapa percaya.

228
00:18:52,965 --> 00:18:54,466
Saya tak faham.

229
00:18:55,384 --> 00:18:57,302
Biar saya jelaskan dengan mudah.

230
00:18:58,220 --> 00:18:59,429
Semua dah termaktub.

231
00:18:59,513 --> 00:19:01,598
Saya dah warisi jawatan ayah.

232
00:19:01,682 --> 00:19:03,559
Sekarang, saya CEO Queens.

233
00:19:03,642 --> 00:19:05,811
Jangan berhelah dengan saya.

234
00:19:06,395 --> 00:19:08,772
Saya tahu awak takkan duduk diam.

235
00:19:08,856 --> 00:19:10,816
Tapi kalau awak cuba buat hal

236
00:19:10,899 --> 00:19:13,110
dengan pengaruhi ayah
atau apa-apa lagi…

237
00:19:14,236 --> 00:19:18,240
Tak susah nak tanam orang sekarang.

238
00:19:19,032 --> 00:19:20,200
Awak faham?

239
00:19:20,701 --> 00:19:25,914
Saya boleh buat awak tak berani
angkat muka lagi.

240
00:19:30,502 --> 00:19:31,503
Se-hyeong.

241
00:19:32,421 --> 00:19:35,257
Saya masih tak faham kata-kata awak.

242
00:19:36,300 --> 00:19:37,342
Jadi, bolehkah…

243
00:19:38,302 --> 00:19:39,344
Awak balik?

244
00:19:39,428 --> 00:19:42,806
Nak terus pura-pura bodoh?

245
00:19:44,099 --> 00:19:46,685
Jangan anggap kami tiada bukti.

246
00:19:48,205 --> 00:19:49,205
Kami ada bukti.

247
00:19:49,229 --> 00:19:50,480
<i>Apa yang awak fikir?</i>

248
00:19:50,564 --> 00:19:53,066
<i>Mereka gembira awak masih hidup.</i>

249
00:19:53,150 --> 00:19:56,153
<i>Ya? Siapa? Mak? Ayah?</i>

250
00:19:56,236 --> 00:19:57,946
<i>Mereka semua.</i>

251
00:19:58,030 --> 00:20:00,824
<i>Ayah, mak, dan abang-abang awak
semua gembira.</i>

252
00:20:01,783 --> 00:20:04,203
Ada rakaman lain juga.

253
00:20:04,328 --> 00:20:06,747
Gambar pun ada. Ada banyak bukti.

254
00:20:11,418 --> 00:20:12,418
Baiklah.

255
00:20:13,462 --> 00:20:15,255
Jadi, menurut awak,

256
00:20:15,339 --> 00:20:17,716
saya ke Korea Utara
dan bertemu Gu Seung-jun.

257
00:20:18,467 --> 00:20:21,803
Kamu tahu segalanya.

258
00:20:22,865 --> 00:20:23,865
Betul.

259
00:20:23,889 --> 00:20:24,889
Tapi…

260
00:20:26,558 --> 00:20:28,602
Awak tak cuba bawa saya balik.

261
00:20:29,622 --> 00:20:30,622
Apa?

262
00:20:30,646 --> 00:20:33,273
Awak nak saya tinggal di sana
selama-lamanya?

263
00:20:33,774 --> 00:20:36,443
Atau awak harap saya dah mati?

264
00:20:37,027 --> 00:20:39,529
Apa yang dia merepek?

265
00:20:39,613 --> 00:20:41,448
Tentulah kami dah cuba.

266
00:20:41,949 --> 00:20:44,910
Tapi, ini bukan main-main.

267
00:20:45,661 --> 00:20:48,580
Kalau tak hati-hati,
seluruh keluarga akan…

268
00:20:48,664 --> 00:20:52,084
Orang kata, ada tiga jenis orang
yang tak patut dilupakan.

269
00:20:52,334 --> 00:20:54,503
Orang yang tolong kita semasa susah,

270
00:20:54,586 --> 00:20:56,630
orang yang tinggalkan kita semasa susah

271
00:20:57,172 --> 00:20:58,172
dan…

272
00:20:58,465 --> 00:21:00,926
Orang yang menyusahkan kita.

273
00:21:02,719 --> 00:21:07,224
Sebab itulah saya takkan
lupakan kamu berdua.

274
00:21:07,975 --> 00:21:09,226
Awak ugut kami?

275
00:21:09,309 --> 00:21:11,186
Berani awak cuba ugut…

276
00:21:11,270 --> 00:21:13,855
Sayang, mari kita balik.

277
00:21:13,939 --> 00:21:17,442
Hei, awak sedar diri, bukan?

278
00:21:17,609 --> 00:21:20,237
Awak cuma bertuah dapat balik.

279
00:21:20,821 --> 00:21:21,947
Jangan buat kacau.

280
00:21:22,030 --> 00:21:23,657
Ini amaran terakhir.

281
00:22:04,698 --> 00:22:05,698
Jangan…

282
00:22:07,034 --> 00:22:09,536
Cakap apa-apa.

283
00:22:10,620 --> 00:22:12,164
Saya terlalu malu.

284
00:22:14,666 --> 00:22:15,959
Saya takkan cakap apa-apa.

285
00:22:35,395 --> 00:22:36,688
Ini lebih baik.

286
00:22:37,981 --> 00:22:39,399
Sunyi.

287
00:22:41,401 --> 00:22:42,569
Hangat.

288
00:22:43,403 --> 00:22:47,741
Buat saya kurang marah.

289
00:22:48,742 --> 00:22:50,369
Tapi saya marah.

290
00:22:51,578 --> 00:22:54,498
Saya hampir
keluar dari persembunyian tadi.

291
00:23:03,924 --> 00:23:04,924
Tapi…

292
00:23:07,094 --> 00:23:08,261
Jangan lupa.

293
00:23:09,304 --> 00:23:11,765
Orang yang awak tak patut lupa

294
00:23:12,891 --> 00:23:15,102
bukan yang dibenci, tapi disayang.

295
00:23:16,019 --> 00:23:18,105
Jangan simpan kebencian dalam hati.

296
00:23:18,688 --> 00:23:22,275
Kelak hati awak luka dan berdarah.

297
00:23:23,902 --> 00:23:25,153
Tiada untungnya.

298
00:23:26,905 --> 00:23:28,698
Saya tahu awak amat benci

299
00:23:29,449 --> 00:23:30,449
kekalahan.

300
00:23:32,119 --> 00:23:33,203
Betul.

301
00:23:34,496 --> 00:23:36,331
Saya usahawan.

302
00:23:36,832 --> 00:23:38,458
Saya paling benci kalah.

303
00:23:38,542 --> 00:23:41,420
Jadi, simpan orang yang awak suka
dalam hati.

304
00:23:42,379 --> 00:23:45,340
Baru dapat makan dan tidur dengan aman,

305
00:23:49,511 --> 00:23:50,846
Walaupun…

306
00:23:53,598 --> 00:23:54,975
Dia tiada di sisi saya?

307
00:23:58,854 --> 00:24:00,147
Ya.

308
00:24:16,580 --> 00:24:17,580
Betul kata awak.

309
00:24:18,039 --> 00:24:21,084
Kalau cukup makan dan tidur,
barulah sihat.

310
00:24:21,793 --> 00:24:24,546
Kalau sihat,
baru boleh kalahkan orang lain.

311
00:24:25,714 --> 00:24:29,259
Itu lebih menguntungkan.

312
00:24:30,927 --> 00:24:32,012
Betul.

313
00:24:46,943 --> 00:24:48,945
Korea Selatan tahu kita datang.

314
00:24:50,197 --> 00:24:54,910
Sebab itulah mereka
buka semua lampu, bukan?

315
00:24:55,535 --> 00:24:57,829
Lampu dibuka sepanjang malam?

316
00:24:58,413 --> 00:24:59,539
Takkan dimatikan?

317
00:25:00,081 --> 00:25:02,834
Benar-benar seperti dalam drama.

318
00:25:03,752 --> 00:25:05,212
Bagaikan tak percaya.

319
00:25:07,380 --> 00:25:09,633
Kalau terang begini,

320
00:25:10,467 --> 00:25:14,095
dapatlah U Pil siapkan
kerja rumahnya setiap hari.

321
00:25:16,848 --> 00:25:18,433
Alangkah bagusnya.

322
00:25:20,060 --> 00:25:24,731
Antara semua bangunan itu,
di mana Kapten Ri berada?

323
00:25:25,232 --> 00:25:26,775
Antara semua bangunan itu,

324
00:25:26,858 --> 00:25:31,321
di mana pula agaknya

325
00:25:31,905 --> 00:25:33,406
kita nak tidur malam ini?

326
00:25:43,792 --> 00:25:45,961
SAUNA ARANG

327
00:25:52,092 --> 00:25:55,220
Kalau syurga itu wujud,
di sinilah tempatnya.

328
00:25:57,222 --> 00:26:00,684
Alangkah bagusnya kalau
dapat bawa mak saya ke sini.

329
00:26:00,767 --> 00:26:04,312
Apabila tengok dalam drama,
saya tak sangka ia begini selesa.

330
00:26:04,396 --> 00:26:06,398
Ini betul-betul selesa.

331
00:26:07,899 --> 00:26:08,899
Komrad…

332
00:26:11,486 --> 00:26:13,321
- Maksud saya, kawan.
- Ya.

333
00:26:13,405 --> 00:26:15,907
Jangan terpesona dengan kapitalisme.

334
00:26:17,284 --> 00:26:19,327
Jangan diperdaya kehangatannya.

335
00:26:19,869 --> 00:26:21,079
- Baik.
- Baik.

336
00:26:23,456 --> 00:26:27,711
Hari ini, kita bayar 12,000 won
seorang untuk masuk.

337
00:26:28,628 --> 00:26:31,339
Pastikan wang itu tak terbazir.

338
00:26:31,923 --> 00:26:34,884
Simpan kehangatan ini
untuk tahan angin sejuk esok.

339
00:26:39,139 --> 00:26:40,265
Sebenarnya…

340
00:26:42,475 --> 00:26:43,560
Saya lapar.

341
00:26:47,814 --> 00:26:51,526
Macam saya cakap,
kita belanjakan 12,000 won seorang

342
00:26:51,610 --> 00:26:53,111
untuk duduk di sini…

343
00:26:59,993 --> 00:27:02,203
Macam mana awak boleh beli?

344
00:27:02,704 --> 00:27:04,039
Saya yang pegang duit.

345
00:27:04,122 --> 00:27:05,707
Saya tak tahu.

346
00:27:05,790 --> 00:27:08,126
Pemilik kedai yang beri.

347
00:27:08,209 --> 00:27:09,878
Katanya, tak perlu bayar.

348
00:27:09,961 --> 00:27:11,171
Betulkah?

349
00:27:11,254 --> 00:27:14,674
Dia beri percuma?

350
00:27:14,758 --> 00:27:15,758
Ya.

351
00:27:16,843 --> 00:27:19,596
Katanya, cuma perlu tunjuk ini.

352
00:27:20,305 --> 00:27:22,932
Kapitalisme sangat pemurah.

353
00:27:23,016 --> 00:27:24,309
Gwang Beom,

354
00:27:24,893 --> 00:27:27,103
mungkin sebab awak kacak.

355
00:27:27,729 --> 00:27:29,939
Kalau begitu,

356
00:27:30,023 --> 00:27:31,524
saya pun patut cuba.

357
00:27:33,234 --> 00:27:34,235
Mari makan.

358
00:27:36,571 --> 00:27:37,572
Terima kasih.

359
00:27:38,365 --> 00:27:39,658
Hati-hati. Panas.

360
00:27:40,742 --> 00:27:41,742
Minumlah.

361
00:28:02,889 --> 00:28:05,392
LOKAR KASUT LELAKI

362
00:28:05,475 --> 00:28:07,519
Terima kasih. Sila datang lagi.

363
00:28:11,815 --> 00:28:15,151
12,000 won untuk kemewahan itu.

364
00:28:15,235 --> 00:28:17,821
Berbaloi juga.

365
00:28:17,904 --> 00:28:19,906
- Memang berbaloi.
- Ya.

366
00:28:26,830 --> 00:28:27,830
Maaf.

367
00:28:28,456 --> 00:28:29,958
Tolong bayar dulu.

368
00:28:32,544 --> 00:28:34,421
Ada yang guna servis lulur.

369
00:28:35,046 --> 00:28:37,132
Jumlahnya 137,000 won.

370
00:28:39,801 --> 00:28:41,386
Siapa yang dilulur?

371
00:28:55,650 --> 00:28:57,736
- Seronoknya.
- Awak dah siap!

372
00:28:59,195 --> 00:29:01,322
- Oh, Tuhan!
- Wol Suk!

373
00:29:01,406 --> 00:29:03,074
Awak nampak cantik.

374
00:29:03,158 --> 00:29:05,535
Awak apa kurangnya?

375
00:29:05,618 --> 00:29:08,288
Baru berhias sedikit,
awak dah nampak anggun.

376
00:29:08,371 --> 00:29:10,623
Kita patut selalu begini.

377
00:29:10,707 --> 00:29:13,918
Betul. Kita tak pernah berhias,

378
00:29:14,002 --> 00:29:17,297
