379
00:29:17,380 --> 00:29:19,549
- Betul.
- Betul?

380
00:29:21,551 --> 00:29:23,762
- Oh, Tuhan.
- Yeong Ae!

381
00:29:25,346 --> 00:29:28,391
- Yeong Ae!
- Tengoklah dia.

382
00:29:29,684 --> 00:29:31,436
Tuhanku!

383
00:29:32,395 --> 00:29:37,108
Yeong Ae, hidung lelaki di sini
akan berdarah kerana awak.

384
00:29:37,192 --> 00:29:38,109
Taklah.

385
00:29:38,193 --> 00:29:39,986
Jangan mengoceh.

386
00:29:40,069 --> 00:29:41,738
- Taklah.
- Tak.

387
00:29:41,821 --> 00:29:45,158
Awak bagaikan bunga yang berkembang
di tengah salji.

388
00:29:45,241 --> 00:29:46,743
Betul.

389
00:29:47,494 --> 00:29:50,288
Jadi, penilik nasib itu bagus?

390
00:29:51,224 --> 00:29:52,224
Bagus.

391
00:29:52,248 --> 00:29:56,836
Sejak lima tahun lepas,
ramalannya tentang suami saya tepat.

392
00:29:57,337 --> 00:29:58,797
- Tepat?
- Tepat?

393
00:29:58,880 --> 00:30:01,508
Suami saya takkan naik pangkat.

394
00:30:02,258 --> 00:30:03,635
Ramalannya tepat.

395
00:30:12,936 --> 00:30:14,437
Awak tak bawa sesiapa?

396
00:30:15,355 --> 00:30:17,482
Tak. Jangan risau.

397
00:30:17,565 --> 00:30:19,526
Malah, kawan kami jaga di luar.

398
00:30:26,407 --> 00:30:27,407
Ertinya, selamat.

399
00:30:27,909 --> 00:30:30,829
Dua tukang tilik ditangkap minggu ini.

400
00:30:30,912 --> 00:30:33,164
Saya tak boleh tidur kerana takut.

401
00:30:33,832 --> 00:30:38,002
Awak tukang tilik.
Tak boleh tilik nasib sendiri?

402
00:30:40,421 --> 00:30:41,421
Hei.

403
00:30:41,840 --> 00:30:45,218
Dia berurusan dengan hantu Selatan.

404
00:30:45,301 --> 00:30:48,054
Jadi dia tak boleh ramal

405
00:30:48,137 --> 00:30:49,931
operasi tentera di sini.

406
00:30:50,014 --> 00:30:51,432
- Betulkah?
- Ya.

407
00:30:51,516 --> 00:30:53,434
Tapi, berkenaan wang, anak,

408
00:30:53,518 --> 00:30:57,438
kerjaya suami dan kesihatan,

409
00:30:57,522 --> 00:31:00,233
dia sangat bagus.

410
00:31:00,316 --> 00:31:02,068
- Betul.
- Ya.

411
00:31:02,151 --> 00:31:04,404
Kalau begitu…

412
00:31:04,988 --> 00:31:09,450
Macam mana nak buat
anak saya rajin belajar?

413
00:31:09,534 --> 00:31:11,619
Saya nak dia belajar perubatan.

414
00:31:11,703 --> 00:31:13,872
Perubatan? Sekejap.

415
00:31:23,298 --> 00:31:24,716
Tiada bunyi pun.

416
00:31:26,634 --> 00:31:28,928
Asalkan roh dapat dengar,

417
00:31:29,012 --> 00:31:31,389
kita tak perlu risau.

418
00:31:31,472 --> 00:31:33,433
- Ya.
- Baik.

419
00:31:33,516 --> 00:31:36,019
Kalau locengnya kuat, pegawai akan dengar.

420
00:31:36,102 --> 00:31:37,729
- Betul.
- Ya.

421
00:31:50,617 --> 00:31:52,201
Habislah kamu semua.

422
00:31:52,285 --> 00:31:54,245
Loghat Korea Selatan.

423
00:31:55,538 --> 00:31:57,081
Suami awak ke tempat jauh.

424
00:31:57,165 --> 00:31:58,958
- Wah!
- Oh, Tuhan.

425
00:31:59,042 --> 00:32:02,754
Dia ada misi di Pyongyang selama sebulan.

426
00:32:02,837 --> 00:32:06,758
Bukan di Pyongyang. Lebih jauh.

427
00:32:06,841 --> 00:32:08,092
- Apa?
- Apa?

428
00:32:09,177 --> 00:32:10,803
Dia tak boleh balik!

429
00:32:11,262 --> 00:32:12,262
- Apa?
- Apa?

430
00:32:12,847 --> 00:32:14,974
Apa maksud awak?

431
00:32:15,058 --> 00:32:16,935
Kenapa dia tak boleh balik?

432
00:32:17,560 --> 00:32:20,396
Awak pun ada masalah sendiri.

433
00:32:21,022 --> 00:32:22,106
Saya?

434
00:32:25,777 --> 00:32:28,529
Pertumpahan darah
akan berlaku di kampung ini.

435
00:32:28,613 --> 00:32:29,697
"Pertumpahan darah"?

436
00:32:31,282 --> 00:32:32,450
Saya takut.

437
00:32:35,453 --> 00:32:37,080
Nak manisan.

438
00:32:37,163 --> 00:32:38,998
Ada di sini.

439
00:32:47,298 --> 00:32:48,298
Kenapa?

440
00:32:49,884 --> 00:32:51,010
Apa awak buat?

441
