Lepaskan saya!

442
00:32:56,140 --> 00:32:58,017
- Apa awak buat?
- Heret dia.

443
00:32:58,101 --> 00:32:59,769
Apa yang awak buat?

444
00:32:59,852 --> 00:33:02,146
Lepaskan saya!

445
00:33:06,776 --> 00:33:08,695
- Apa semua ini?
- Heret dia!

446
00:33:09,195 --> 00:33:11,364
Lepaskan saya!

447
00:33:15,201 --> 00:33:16,703
Lepaskan saya!

448
00:33:22,417 --> 00:33:24,168
Kemas beg awak cepat.

449
00:33:25,003 --> 00:33:27,422
Apa? Kemas apa?

450
00:33:27,505 --> 00:33:28,423
Cepat!

451
00:33:28,506 --> 00:33:29,632
Kenapa?

452
00:33:29,716 --> 00:33:32,051
Cho Cheol Gang dah ditangkap.

453
00:33:32,135 --> 00:33:33,469
Kerana apa?

454
00:33:33,553 --> 00:33:34,721
Semuanya.

455
00:33:34,804 --> 00:33:37,181
Bisnes aga orang ini pun dah diketahui.

456
00:33:37,265 --> 00:33:38,850
Jadi?

457
00:33:39,642 --> 00:33:42,812
Ada kemalangan waktu dia dipindahkan.

458
00:33:44,731 --> 00:33:46,232
Hidup matinya tak diketahui.

459
00:33:46,315 --> 00:33:48,484
Kita akan mati jika ditangkap.

460
00:33:48,568 --> 00:33:53,406
Mati? Apa yang sedang berlaku?

461
00:33:53,489 --> 00:33:55,324
Semua ini sebab Ri Jeong Hyeok.

462
00:33:55,408 --> 00:33:57,660
Kalau awak tak tolong Ri Jeong Hyeok,

463
00:33:57,744 --> 00:33:59,996
Cho Cheol Gang takkan ditangkap.

464
00:34:00,079 --> 00:34:02,290
Awak salahkan saya?

465
00:34:02,373 --> 00:34:05,835
