466
00:34:05,960 --> 00:34:07,295
Abang.

467
00:34:07,378 --> 00:34:09,255
Jangan tinggalkan saya.

468
00:34:09,338 --> 00:34:10,840
Cepatlah kemas barang!

469
00:34:11,674 --> 00:34:13,551
Dah siap.

470
00:34:15,678 --> 00:34:16,929
En. Cheon Su Bok.

471
00:34:20,058 --> 00:34:21,184
Lepaskan saya!

