kompeni saya ditukar kembali.</i>

485
00:35:22,370 --> 00:35:25,081
<i>Saya berjanji akan balik sebelum itu.</i>

486
00:35:26,082 --> 00:35:27,375
<i>Tak usahlah risau.</i>

487
00:35:52,191 --> 00:35:55,069
