741
00:53:52,729 --> 00:53:54,731
- Oh, Tuhan.
- Oh, Tuhan.

742
00:53:55,232 --> 00:53:57,776
- Sukar dipercayai.
- Apa semua ini?

743
00:54:04,032 --> 00:54:05,992
Saya dah selamatkan awak.

744
00:54:06,076 --> 00:54:07,494
Jangan merepek.

745
00:54:08,828 --> 00:54:11,790
Ada manisan di dalam kereta?

746
00:54:12,540 --> 00:54:14,793
Dari mana awak belajar perkataan itu?

747
00:54:14,876 --> 00:54:17,003
Dari mana saya belajar tak penting.

748
00:54:17,087 --> 00:54:18,380
Betul,

749
00:54:18,463 --> 00:54:21,967
yang penting,
kita perlukan manisan apabila muram.

750
00:54:22,050 --> 00:54:23,593
Coklat atau gula-gula.

751
00:54:23,677 --> 00:54:25,011
- Ada?
- Tiada.

752
00:54:29,349 --> 00:54:31,059
Ada kedai serbaneka di sini?

753
00:54:38,650 --> 00:54:40,318
Hei, mari sini.

754
00:54:49,077 --> 00:54:50,495
SEKURITI

755
00:54:55,583 --> 00:54:57,043
Hei.

756
00:55:01,423 --> 00:55:03,508
Mari makan bersama.

757
00:55:03,591 --> 00:55:05,760
Mesyuarat akan habis lewat hari ini.

758
00:55:06,761 --> 00:55:09,556
Saya akan makan dengan Pengerusi Yoon…

759
00:55:09,639 --> 00:55:12,851
- Dia tak makan dengan orang.
- Dia belum tahu

760
00:55:12,934 --> 00:55:15,061
peraturan di sini.

761
00:55:15,145 --> 00:55:16,313
Susahlah.

762
00:55:16,396 --> 00:55:18,189
Cik Yoon makan seorang diri.

763
00:55:18,273 --> 00:55:21,568
Dia tak suka ada teman makan
atau bercakap.

764
00:55:22,110 --> 00:55:23,611
Dia tak suka warna itu.

765
00:55:23,695 --> 00:55:25,113
Dia benci.

766
00:55:25,697 --> 00:55:26,697
Dia suka.

767
00:55:27,115 --> 00:55:28,908
Tak mungkin.

768
00:55:29,409 --> 00:55:31,244
Awak langsung tak kenal dia.

769
00:55:31,911 --> 00:55:33,747
Bukanlah tak kenal langsung.

770
00:55:34,748 --> 00:55:35,748
Apa awak cakap?

771
00:55:36,207 --> 00:55:39,544
Dia sensitif macam kucing.

772
00:55:39,627 --> 00:55:42,255
Dia cuma makan telur
yang direbus 8 minit 27 saat.

773
00:55:42,339 --> 00:55:46,051
Kalau direbus 8 minit 30 saat,
dia akan kata terlalu kering.

774
00:55:46,134 --> 00:55:47,886
Dia tahu.

775
00:55:55,518 --> 00:55:57,771
Awak kena kaji cita rasa dia.

776
00:55:57,854 --> 00:56:00,106
Barulah dapat bekerja lama di sini.

777
00:56:00,190 --> 00:56:02,984
Anggap ini nasihat senior.

778
00:56:07,572 --> 00:56:10,492
Saya tak tahu cita rasa awak?

779
00:56:10,575 --> 00:56:11,826
Apa maksud awak?

780
00:56:12,660 --> 00:56:14,788
Pekerja awak cukup kenal awak.

781
00:56:14,871 --> 00:56:16,873
Mereka tahu cara rebus telur
kesukaan awak.

782
00:56:17,624 --> 00:56:19,793
Itu tak penting.

783
00:56:20,835 --> 00:56:24,005
Awak yang paling tahu cita rasa saya.

784
00:56:26,341 --> 00:56:27,759
Apa yang awak suka?

785
00:56:29,427 --> 00:56:30,428
Awak.

786
00:56:31,638 --> 00:56:34,140
Saya pernah cakap
ketika kita pertama kali bertemu.

787
00:56:34,224 --> 00:56:36,184
Awak sangat kacak bagi saya.

788
00:56:39,437 --> 00:56:41,731
Pura-pura tak tahu pula?

789
00:57:11,845 --> 00:57:14,764
Awak sepatutnya tinggal di sini
selepas berkahwin?

790
00:57:15,598 --> 00:57:18,059
Tak sangka awak lelaki pertama

791
00:57:18,560 --> 00:57:20,687
yang masuk ke sini.

792
00:57:20,770 --> 00:57:24,315
Saya sendiri pun tak sangka.

793
00:57:24,399 --> 00:57:26,693
Tinggallah di sini beberapa hari,

794
00:57:27,652 --> 00:57:28,903
tapi, tak boleh lama.

795
00:57:28,987 --> 00:57:30,447
Takkan lama.

796
00:57:30,530 --> 00:57:33,616
Saya sepatutnya naik pesawat hari ini.

797
00:57:33,700 --> 00:57:36,619
Tapi ada hal,
jadi kena tunggu beberapa hari.

798
00:57:37,120 --> 00:57:38,746
Takkan lama di sini.

799
00:57:38,830 --> 00:57:41,040
Jangan tinggalkan sebarang kesan.

800
00:57:41,583 --> 00:57:44,252
Pastikan awak cuma bernafas di sini.

801
00:57:44,961 --> 00:57:45,961
Okey.

802
00:57:52,802 --> 00:57:54,262
Saya balik dulu.

803
00:57:54,846 --> 00:57:56,973
Saya akan bawa balik kereta itu.

804
00:57:57,056 --> 00:58:01,144
Matikan lampu sepuluh minit lagi.
Mungkin ada pemeriksaan mengejut.

805
00:58:01,895 --> 00:58:02,895
Nak balik terus?

806
00:58:02,937 --> 00:58:05,023
Awak tak lapar? Saya lapar.

807
00:58:06,858 --> 00:58:07,901
Nak mi segera?

808
00:58:15,783 --> 00:58:19,704
Ini kali pertama saya makan mi segera
dengan perempuan.

809
00:58:19,787 --> 00:58:21,331
Jangan fikir bukan-bukan.

810
00:58:21,414 --> 00:58:23,082
Tak.

811
00:58:23,166 --> 00:58:26,586
Mi segera ada lambang sosial tersendiri.

812
00:58:28,087 --> 00:58:29,172
Lambang apa?

813
00:58:30,465 --> 00:58:31,925
"Nak makan mi segera?"

814
00:58:32,008 --> 00:58:35,845
Orang tak cakap begini di Korea Selatan.

815
00:58:35,929 --> 00:58:37,680
Saya tak kisah,

816
00:58:37,764 --> 00:58:41,392
tapi kalau lelaki
kata begitu kepada awak,

817
00:58:41,976 --> 00:58:43,937
awak mesti tolak mentah-mentah.

818
00:58:46,856 --> 00:58:48,566
Kenapa mesti tolak?

819
00:58:50,735 --> 00:58:51,903
Saya suka.

820
00:58:56,157 --> 00:58:57,158
Apa?

821
00:58:57,742 --> 00:58:59,786
Awak suka apa? Mi segera?

822
00:59:00,578 --> 00:59:02,705
Lelaki yang bertanya itu?

823
00:59:04,165 --> 00:59:05,165
Atau…

824
00:59:07,126 --> 00:59:08,126
Saya?

825
00:59:22,350 --> 00:59:23,768
Kenapa dia senyum?

826
00:59:24,852 --> 00:59:26,145
Saya buat lawak?

827
00:59:33,111 --> 00:59:35,196
Tapi, tak lawak pun.

828
00:59:43,413 --> 00:59:44,789
Kenapa benda ini

829
00:59:46,040 --> 00:59:47,584
buat saya tertanya-tanya?

830
00:59:53,631 --> 00:59:56,301
Baiklah, saya akan tanya dia.

831
00:59:58,344 --> 01:00:01,389
Telefon dia. Barulah berani.

832
01:00:01,931 --> 01:00:05,101
Saya cuma nak tanya
punca dia tersenyum tadi.

833
01:00:07,937 --> 01:00:11,065
<i>Nombor yang anda dail tak dapat dihubungi.</i>

834
01:00:14,986 --> 01:00:15,987
Dah tidur?

835
01:00:17,196 --> 01:00:18,197
Awalnya?

836
01:00:19,490 --> 01:00:21,492
Mungkin dia belum sampai ke rumah.

837
01:00:22,660 --> 01:00:24,162
Sebab itu dia tak jawab?

838
01:00:27,582 --> 01:00:29,667
Atau dia sengaja tak mahu angkat?

839
01:00:30,793 --> 01:00:31,793
Kenapa?

840
01:00:33,171 --> 01:00:34,422
Dia jual mahal?

841
01:00:38,343 --> 01:00:39,343
Kenapa?

842
01:00:46,059 --> 01:00:48,561
Belum nampak rekod panggilan saya?

843
01:00:49,312 --> 01:00:51,105
Hari dah terang.

844
01:00:53,483 --> 01:00:54,984
Dia bangun lewat?

845
01:00:55,568 --> 01:00:57,195
Tak payah fikir.

846
01:00:59,322 --> 01:01:01,699
Itu perkara kecil.

847
01:01:04,410 --> 01:01:06,037
Tentu sebab saya tak cukup makan.

848
01:01:24,389 --> 01:01:26,224
- Helo.
- Kenapa telefon saya?

849
01:01:26,808 --> 01:01:28,768
Saya telefon awak?

850
01:01:29,352 --> 01:01:31,521
Mungkin tersilap tekan.

851
01:01:32,105 --> 01:01:34,857
Awak telefon saya
sebaik saja bangun tidur?

852
01:01:34,941 --> 01:01:36,234
Tak apalah kalau begitu.

853
01:01:36,317 --> 01:01:37,902
Tunggu!

854
01:01:39,612 --> 01:01:41,364
Nak cakap apa-apa lagi?

855
01:01:43,074 --> 01:01:44,409
Awak sedang buat apa?

856
01:01:44,492 --> 01:01:47,495
Maksud saya, apa saya nak buat hari ini?

857
01:01:48,705 --> 01:01:50,456
Kenapa tanya saya?

858
01:01:50,540 --> 01:01:53,835
Saya tiada tempat bertanya.
Saya tak kenal orang lain.

859
01:01:53,918 --> 01:01:57,630
Ada perkara yang saya nak tanya awak.
Patutkah saya ke sana?

860
01:01:57,714 --> 01:01:59,716
Tapi, jauh, dan saya tiada kereta.

861
01:02:00,258 --> 01:02:01,300
Awak bawa balik.

862
01:02:02,593 --> 01:02:04,345
- Jadi?
- Awaklah yang datang.

863
01:02:07,682 --> 01:02:08,766
Helo?

864
01:02:10,059 --> 01:02:11,227
Helo?

865
01:02:13,020 --> 01:02:14,020
Dia letak?

866
01:02:14,731 --> 01:02:16,649
Dia tak cakap, "Saya nak letak."

867
01:02:16,733 --> 01:02:18,109
Terputus?

868
01:02:18,192 --> 01:02:20,361
Isyarat di sini lemah?

869
01:02:20,862 --> 01:02:21,863
Apa berlaku?

870
01:02:23,573 --> 01:02:24,866
Kenapa dengan saya?

871
01:02:25,491 --> 01:02:28,035
Hei, kenapa dengan awak?

872
01:02:28,119 --> 01:02:29,871
Saya suruh awak jaga Dan

873
01:02:29,954 --> 01:02:31,414
dan pantau dia!

874
01:02:31,497 --> 01:02:36,627
Kakak, tanyalah askar di kem saya?

875
01:02:36,711 --> 01:02:39,088
Mereka ada nampak saya di sana?

876
01:02:39,172 --> 01:02:43,092
Sejak Dan balik, saya tak pernah ke kem.

877
01:02:43,176 --> 01:02:46,512
Jadi, macam mana
boleh terlepas perkara ini?

878
01:02:46,596 --> 01:02:49,348
<i>Anak pemilik Gedung Serbaneka Pyongyang…</i>

879
01:02:49,432 --> 01:02:50,266
Apa ini?

880
01:02:50,349 --> 01:02:54,187
<i>Telah putus tunang dengan Ri Jeong Hyeok</i>

881
01:02:54,270 --> 01:02:56,022
<i>kerana hubungannya dengan lelaki lain.</i>

882
01:02:56,105 --> 01:02:57,607
Lelaki ini

883
01:02:58,524 --> 01:02:59,609
lelaki kelmarin?

884
01:02:59,692 --> 01:03:02,320
Itu yang saya nak awak tanya dia!

885
01:03:02,403 --> 01:03:05,072
Baiklah. Sudah!

886
01:03:10,661 --> 01:03:11,788
Dan.

887
01:03:11,871 --> 01:03:15,082
Mak nak bincang dengan kamu.

888
01:03:15,792 --> 01:03:18,085
Pak cik kamu nampak…

889
01:03:18,961 --> 01:03:19,961
Cakaplah.

890
01:03:20,838 --> 01:03:25,134
Ingat lelaki di hotel itu?

891
01:03:25,218 --> 01:03:26,761
Komrad Al.

892
01:03:27,720 --> 01:03:29,055
Alberto.

893
01:03:31,766 --> 01:03:32,850
- Kenapa?
- Dia…

894
01:03:35,895 --> 01:03:40,358
Mak awak dengar khabar angin

895
01:03:40,441 --> 01:03:42,443
semasa bersarapan tadi.

896
01:03:44,362 --> 01:03:45,571
Sambunglah.

897
01:03:45,655 --> 01:03:47,114
Tak guna…

898
01:03:47,824 --> 01:03:50,701
Begini, mak dengar

899
01:03:51,369 --> 01:03:54,914
semasa kamu berjumpa kawan-kawan semalam,

900
01:03:54,997 --> 01:03:58,084
ada lelaki jemput kamu.

901
01:03:58,167 --> 01:04:02,588
Dia Komrad Al yang pak cik kamu nampak

902
01:04:02,672 --> 01:04:04,298
- kelmarin?
- Mak.

903
01:04:05,258 --> 01:04:06,634
Ya. Apa?

904
01:04:07,301 --> 01:04:09,554
Mak sedia mendengar. Cakaplah.

905
01:04:11,597 --> 01:04:13,516
Saya nak keluar sekejap.

906
01:04:13,599 --> 01:04:15,643
Sekarang? Nak mak temankan?

907
01:04:18,896 --> 01:04:19,896
Tak nak.

908
01:04:20,690 --> 01:04:21,816
Selamat jalan.

909
01:04:23,985 --> 01:04:25,152
Sah.

910
01:04:25,528 --> 01:04:27,196
Apa? Hubungan sulit?

911
01:04:27,280 --> 01:04:28,698
Bukan, cinta.

912
01:04:28,781 --> 01:04:33,619
Dan bukannya isteri Ri Jeong Hyeok.

913
01:04:33,703 --> 01:04:35,037
Hubungan sulit apa?

914
01:04:36,372 --> 01:04:41,085
Kalau itu pilihan hatinya, saya sokong.

915
01:04:42,128 --> 01:04:43,546
- Betul?
- Ya.

916
01:04:43,629 --> 01:04:46,549
Awak tak kenal pun lelaki itu!

917
01:04:46,632 --> 01:04:49,844
Saya tak kisah

918
01:04:49,969 --> 01:04:52,972
asalkan Alberto bukan pencuri atau penipu.

919
01:05:01,022 --> 01:05:02,064
Helo.

920
01:05:02,565 --> 01:05:03,691
Turunlah.

921
01:05:04,400 --> 01:05:05,943
Awak dah sampai?

922
01:05:22,835 --> 01:05:23,961
Pandang apa?

923
01:05:25,148 --> 01:05:26,148
Turun.

924
01:05:26,172 --> 01:05:28,299
Tunggu sekejap.

925
01:05:28,382 --> 01:05:30,843
Beri saya sepuluh minit.
Tak, lima minit.

926
01:05:30,927 --> 01:05:32,470
Saya beri tiga minit.

927
01:05:36,015 --> 01:05:37,015
Mak.

928
01:05:38,017 --> 01:05:41,812
Anak sulung mak
datang membawa maklumat penting.

929
01:05:42,313 --> 01:05:44,941
Mak letih. Pendekkan.

930
01:05:45,733 --> 01:05:49,195
Ini terlalu menggemparkan.
Mana boleh pendekkan?

931
01:05:49,278 --> 01:05:52,949
Ini tentang perkara yang berlaku
selepas Seri hilang

932
01:05:53,032 --> 01:05:57,411
dan cara dia dapat pulang dengan selamat
selepas sebulan.

933
01:05:57,495 --> 01:05:58,788
Seri…

934
01:05:59,246 --> 01:06:01,374
- Dia di Korea Utara.
- Hei.

935
01:06:02,500 --> 01:06:04,085
Apa kamu kata?

936
01:06:04,168 --> 01:06:07,046
Korea Utara.
Negara yang selalu masuk berita.

937
01:06:07,129 --> 01:06:09,715
Dia bersusah-payah mencari maklumat ini.

938
01:06:09,799 --> 01:06:10,925
Apa yang kamu…

939
01:06:11,008 --> 01:06:13,052
Jangan terkejut sekarang.

940
01:06:13,135 --> 01:06:15,054
Ada yang lebih mengejutkan.

941
01:06:15,137 --> 01:06:18,099
Yoon Se-hyeong tak guna itu
dah tahu semua ini.

942
01:06:18,182 --> 01:06:19,892
Si dubuk itu!

943
01:06:19,976 --> 01:06:22,436
- Apa?
- Walaupun dia dah tahu…

944
01:06:22,520 --> 01:06:24,355
Dia rahsiakan.

945
01:06:24,438 --> 01:06:27,608
Dia nak biar adik saya
mati di tempat menakutkan itu.

946
01:06:27,692 --> 01:06:29,694
Memang itu yang dia mahu.

947
01:06:29,777 --> 01:06:30,778
Saya pasti.

948
01:06:31,362 --> 01:06:34,365
Sanggup dia buat begitu
untuk jadi pewaris?

949
01:06:35,032 --> 01:06:40,371
Mak, patutkah orang tak berhati perut itu

950
01:06:40,454 --> 01:06:42,456
diberi kuasa?

951
01:06:42,957 --> 01:06:44,458
Kamu dah sahkan hal ini?

952
01:06:44,542 --> 01:06:46,293
Mestilah.

953
01:06:49,255 --> 01:06:50,464
Sumbernya Pengurus Oh.

954
01:06:52,174 --> 01:06:54,468
<i>Dia pemberi maklumat
Gu Seung-jun di China.</i>

955
01:06:54,552 --> 01:06:58,097
<i>Dia dah beberapa kali
berjumpa Se-hyeong dan Sang-a,</i>

956
01:06:58,180 --> 01:07:00,766
<i>jadi saya cuba korek maklumat ini.</i>

957
01:07:01,600 --> 01:07:03,936
<i>Baru-baru ini, Pengurus Oh ke China.</i>

958
01:07:04,895 --> 01:07:06,856
<i>Entah apa rancangannya.</i>

959
01:07:07,356 --> 01:07:09,984
<i>Saya rasa ia berkaitan kepulangan Seri,</i>

960
01:07:10,526 --> 01:07:12,570
<i>jadi saya siasat.</i>

961
01:07:15,406 --> 01:07:16,615
Encik.

962
01:07:17,366 --> 01:07:19,493
Khabarnya begitulah.

963
01:07:21,162 --> 01:07:22,413
Petang ini?

964
01:07:22,496 --> 01:07:23,497
Boleh.

965
01:07:24,373 --> 01:07:26,375
Kita perlu berbincang

966
01:07:26,459 --> 01:07:27,960
dan buat pengiraan.

967
01:07:29,170 --> 01:07:30,379
Nak bertemu di mana?

968
01:07:32,465 --> 01:07:34,300
Tengok.

969
01:07:34,383 --> 01:07:37,428
Saya pun terkejut tadi.

970
01:07:38,846 --> 01:07:41,348
LELAKI KACAK YANG TINGGI BUDI PEKERTI

971
01:07:41,432 --> 01:07:42,475
Siapa rakam?

972
01:07:42,558 --> 01:07:44,935
Ada orang rakam guna telefon bimbit.

973
01:07:45,019 --> 01:07:47,730
Sebab inilah saya suruh awak berhati-hati.

974
01:07:49,023 --> 01:07:50,566
Tak sangka jadi begini,

975
01:07:51,525 --> 01:07:52,735
Saya yang cuai.

976
01:07:52,818 --> 01:07:54,779
Saya cuma pegangkan pintu.

977
01:07:54,862 --> 01:07:57,198
Tuhanku. Ia dah tular.

978
01:07:57,281 --> 01:07:59,075
<i>Penjaga pintu itu budiman.</i>

979
01:07:59,158 --> 01:08:00,743
<i>Dia bukan penjaga pintu.</i>

980
01:08:00,826 --> 01:08:03,871
- <i>Tinggi.</i>
- Apa maksud "jejaka pujaan"?

981
01:08:03,954 --> 01:08:06,874
Maksudnya, awak kacak.

982
01:08:08,334 --> 01:08:10,169
Oh, begitu.

983
01:08:10,753 --> 01:08:11,837
Itu maksudnya.

984
01:08:14,006 --> 01:08:15,925
Dia pun cakap begitu.

985
01:08:18,469 --> 01:08:19,469
Awak suka?

986
01:08:21,263 --> 01:08:22,263
Tak.

987
01:08:22,640 --> 01:08:24,225
Apa-apalah.

988
01:08:25,392 --> 01:08:27,520
Apa maksud "L.A.T."?

989
01:08:28,312 --> 01:08:30,731
Entah. Apa maksudnya?

990
01:08:31,607 --> 01:08:33,776
"Lelaki Anugerah Tuhan…"

991
01:08:38,405 --> 01:08:39,490
Amboi, seronoknya?

992
01:08:40,199 --> 01:08:41,325
Nak duduk dan baca?

993
01:08:42,159 --> 01:08:43,160
Boleh juga.

994
01:08:43,619 --> 01:08:45,204
Tak payah. Berdiri saja.

995
01:08:48,916 --> 01:08:50,584
Saya nak buat kerja.

996
01:08:59,760 --> 01:09:02,096
Jeong Hyeok, saya nak buat kerja.

997
01:09:11,313 --> 01:09:12,648
Awak ada telefon?

998
01:09:12,731 --> 01:09:14,859
Bila awak beli?

999
01:09:14,942 --> 01:09:18,112
Satu lagi,
siapa yang telefon awak di sini?

1000
01:09:18,821 --> 01:09:19,821
Sekejap.

1001
01:09:25,661 --> 01:09:28,080
Dah buat janji temu
dengan Cho Cheol Gang?

1002
01:09:28,164 --> 01:09:29,290
Di mana?

1003
01:09:40,509 --> 01:09:42,761
Saya kena keluar petang ini.

1004
01:09:43,429 --> 01:09:45,181
Ke mana?

1005
01:09:46,724 --> 01:09:50,019
Awak dah tahu lokasi Cho Cheol Gang?

1006
01:09:51,395 --> 01:09:52,563
Belum.

1007
01:09:53,689 --> 01:09:56,025
Dia akan berjumpa broker.
Saya akan tengok.

1008
01:09:57,651 --> 01:09:58,903
Biar saya hantarkan.

1009
01:09:58,986 --> 01:10:00,237
Tidak.

1010
01:10:01,322 --> 01:10:02,740
Itu berbahaya.

1011
01:10:03,407 --> 01:10:05,159
Ini Seoul, bukan Pyongyang.

1012
01:10:05,659 --> 01:10:08,621
Awak tak patut berjalan sendirian.

1013
01:10:10,039 --> 01:10:11,040
Memang berbahaya.

1014
01:10:12,583 --> 01:10:15,211
Sebab itulah saya tak boleh bawa awak.

1015
01:10:16,086 --> 01:10:19,882
Kalau saya dapat tangkap dia,
saya akan balik

1016
01:10:22,176 --> 01:10:23,385
malam ini juga.

1017
01:10:24,678 --> 01:10:25,721
Balik?

1018
01:10:27,306 --> 01:10:29,266
Saya tak dapat bertemu awak lagi?

1019
01:10:31,685 --> 01:10:33,229
Takkan sempat.

1020
01:10:39,026 --> 01:10:40,026
Betul juga.

1021
01:10:41,195 --> 01:10:43,405
Awak tak tahu situasi di sana.

1022
01:10:45,032 --> 01:10:46,575
Saya faham.

1023
01:10:50,287 --> 01:10:51,288
Tapi…

1024
01:10:54,917 --> 01:10:58,879
Kalau tak dapat berjumpa lagi pun

1025
01:11:00,714 --> 01:11:02,716
saya nak dengar suara awak.

1026
01:11:08,013 --> 01:11:09,431
Beri saya telefon awak.

1027
01:11:15,229 --> 01:11:16,229
Ini nombor saya.

1028
01:11:18,107 --> 01:11:23,195
Saya muat turun aplikasi
untuk kesan lokasi masing-masing…

1029
01:11:25,114 --> 01:11:26,532
Sekiranya perlu.

1030
01:14:34,845 --> 01:14:36,054
Dia tak apa-apa?

1031
01:14:40,642 --> 01:14:41,643
<i>Awak tak apa-apa?</i>

1032
01:14:42,144 --> 01:14:44,313
<i>Kalau susah hendak balik,</i>

1033
01:14:44,396 --> 01:14:45,689
<i>saya boleh jemput.</i>

1034
01:14:54,948 --> 01:14:56,950
SEKURITI

1035
01:16:58,989 --> 01:17:00,407
Mana kru Animal Farm?

1036
01:17:00,991 --> 01:17:03,869
Mereka patut buat episod tentang saya.

1037
01:18:04,262 --> 01:18:06,264
BUAT PANGGILAN

1038
01:18:18,652 --> 01:18:20,946
LOKASI YOON SERI
SE-RI'S CHOICE

1039
01:19:51,661 --> 01:19:52,704
Jangan datang.

1040
01:20:12,182 --> 01:20:13,308
Kenapa tak angkat…

1041
01:20:13,391 --> 01:20:14,935
<i>Ri Jeong Hyeok.</i>

1042
01:20:15,852 --> 01:20:16,937
<i>Gembira</i>

1043
01:20:18,104 --> 01:20:20,148
<i>dapat berjumpa di Korea Selatan.</i>

1044
01:20:20,649 --> 01:20:23,443
<i>Tak sangka awak benar-benar datang.</i>

1045
01:20:23,527 --> 01:20:25,737
Mana awak dapat telefon ini?

1046
01:20:25,821 --> 01:20:29,741
<i>Saya dengan Yoon Seri.</i>

1047
01:20:32,244 --> 01:20:35,664
<i>Awak tahu dia tak boleh
telefon polis, bukan?</i>

1048
01:20:36,581 --> 01:20:38,416
<i>Saya tak boleh tunggu lama.</i>

1049
01:20:39,626 --> 01:20:41,545
<i>Jangan letak. Terus ke sini.</i>

1050
01:21:10,050 --> 01:21:11,050
Awak di mana?

1051
01:21:11,074 --> 01:21:13,451
<i>Tak perlu tahu.</i>

1052
01:21:13,535 --> 01:21:15,328
<i>Saya nampak awak.</i>

1053
01:21:17,414 --> 01:21:18,498
<i>Angkat tangan.</i>

1054
01:21:23,670 --> 01:21:28,258
<i>Kalau awak cuba berhelah,
saya akan tembak dia.</i>

1055
01:21:29,551 --> 01:21:31,303
Pandang depan, jalan terus.

1056
01:21:31,386 --> 01:21:33,889
Kalau awak sentuh rambut dia sekalipun,

1057
01:21:34,723 --> 01:21:36,224
saya akan bunuh awak.

1058
01:21:36,308 --> 01:21:41,271
Cakaplah sesuka hati sebelum awak mati.

1059
01:21:54,618 --> 01:21:56,244
Cho Cheol Gang!

1060
01:21:56,912 --> 01:21:58,204
Jangan merepek!

1061
01:21:59,998 --> 01:22:01,625
Jeong Hyeok, lari.

1062
01:22:01,708 --> 01:22:04,502
Dia tipu. Dia ada pistol.

1063
01:22:09,049 --> 01:22:11,968
Saya tak apa-apa. Lari!

1064
01:23:51,568 --> 01:23:54,487
TUJUH TAHUN LALU

1065
01:24:42,869 --> 01:24:46,498
Saya nak manisan.

1066
01:24:59,803 --> 01:25:01,262
Sedap.

1067
01:25:01,387 --> 01:25:04,224
Apabila kita marah atau murung,
ia menenangkan.

1068
01:25:07,102 --> 01:25:08,394
Bukan orang Korea?

1069
01:25:08,478 --> 01:25:09,521
Maaf.

1070
01:25:28,414 --> 01:25:30,083
Yang lelaki, senyum sedikit.

1071
01:25:36,339 --> 01:25:37,632
Kamu nampak sepadan.

1072
01:26:19,048 --> 01:26:21,259
<i>Awak kata awak ke Cheongdam-dong</i>

1073
01:26:21,342 --> 01:26:23,178
<i>untuk cari rumah Seri.</i>

1074
01:26:23,261 --> 01:26:24,304
Berhenti di situ.

1075
01:26:24,387 --> 01:26:27,599
<i>Susah betul nak cari mereka berdua.</i>

1076
01:26:28,266 --> 01:26:29,726
<i>Dan tak pulang semalam?</i>

1077
01:26:29,809 --> 01:26:30,977
Oh, Tuhan!

1078
01:26:31,060 --> 01:26:32,353
<i>Awak fikir saya tak tahu</i>

1079
01:26:32,437 --> 01:26:34,522
<i>siapa awak di Selatan?</i>

1080
01:26:34,606 --> 01:26:37,942
Dengan pakaian ini,
tiada sesiapa akan pandang aneh kita.

1081
01:26:38,026 --> 01:26:42,155
Saya ada kejutan untuk kamu.

1082
01:26:42,238 --> 01:26:46,034
Saya kena bawa dia balik
untuk sahkan sesuatu.

1083
01:26:46,117 --> 01:26:48,995
<i>Saya nak tinggal di sini dengan awak.</i>

1084
01:26:49,495 --> 01:26:51,497
Terjemahan sari kata oleh Ris

